This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-kivy-phytec layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============

- meta-openembedded
- meta-phytec
- meta-ampliphy
- Bitbake

Maintainer
==========

If you experience any problem with this software, please contact our <support@phytec.de> or the maintainer directly. 

The maintainer of this layer is Martin Schwan <m.schwan@phytec.de>. 

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-kivy-phytec layer to your build
 II. Misc


I. Adding the meta-phykivy layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-kivy-phytec'

II. Misc
========

This layer contains:
- a fix for sdl2 to make it work with OPENGL ES I
- patches for Kivy recipe
- Kivy demo service
- a recipe to import PHYTEC pictures on the target (phytecvisuals)
- an image recipe
